title:
High Performance 
3 Flute Square End 
1/4" Cutting Diameter
description:
Designed for eye-popping high performance chimpfering and countersinking in all materials. The Lemur high performance chamfer line is designed in 3 flute (Zrn coated) and 5 flute (GMS² coated) configurations and “drop the mic” while achieving maximum finish quality in materials up to 55 Rc.
Available in special diameters, lengths and completely resharpenable.

Tolerances

  • Cut Dia +.000/-.002
  • Shank Dia -.0001/-.0005
  • LOC +.025/+.050
  • OAL +/-.050
